name: Amazing Sound! Air Transat A330-243 [C-GTSI] Crisp Winter Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Winter is not always the most ideal season for spotting, from low temperatures to overcast and snowy conditions, but crystal clear days like this are just perfect! Here we have an Air Transat A330 taxiing and taking off from Calgary International Airport back in December for Cancun. ATC is included, along with some phenomenal Trent 700 howling! Enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
